      "back": "Mitochondria"
    },
    {
      "front": "All known living organisms are composed of which basic structures?",
      "back": "Cells"
    },
    {
      "front": "What is the primary function associated with mitochondria within a cell?",
      "back": "Producing ATP"
    },
    {
      "front": "If cells are the basic unit of life, what specific organelle is vital for generating the cell's energy currency?",
      "back": "Mitochondria"
    },
    {
      "front": "What does ATP stand for, and where is it primarily produced?",
      "back": "Adenosine Triphosphate; produced by mitochondria."
    },
